description:
AnubisFX x TANKUSS : 𝙁𝘼𝙇𝙇𝙀𝙉ӄɨռɢ゜⁽²⁰²²⁾

[𝙁𝘼𝙇𝙇𝙀𝙉ӄɨռɢ] The core concept stems from honoring and referencing some our idols who have created huge waves in their genre of Art. The idols we look up to were just humans too even if we had never met them, but with their talent and extraordinary creativity they influenced us humans still walking the earth. Through their Art, their legacy and influence will live on. Just how @tankuss and my Art will live on for years to come as long as the internet is around. 𝙁𝘼𝙇𝙇𝙀𝙉ӄɨռɢ is a tribute and inspired by two Kings that roamed this earth and pored their heart and soul into their craft: Daniel Dumile “MF DOOM” & Jean-Michel Basquiat “BASQUIAT”. Unfortunately the inevitable FATE will come, where we too will become 𝙁𝘼𝙇𝙇𝙀𝙉ӄɨռɢs.
